parameters:
It seems like something happened... Would you like
to go and check the throne?

Lord Konoha! You've returned! Ah, the king too!!!
Your appearance has also returned!

Well, it's great that things are peaceful and we
don't really need anything special right now, but
we still rely on our business to make a living.

The dark demon won't revive anymore... Phew,
that's a relief~

The other day, I witnessed the king reading a
naughty book, but I couldn't bring myself to say
anything.
This is the men's bathing area...

It's not a big deal, it's not like it's going to
decrease or anything.

Lately, I've been eating too much... and it's made
me sluggish...

The soldiers' meal preparation is very, very
difficult!! Ohohohoho!

What does ' \c[2]Ruder\c[0]' mean? It mainly
refers to a general term for thieves, barbarians,
and outlaws. Pirates do not belong to this
category as they do not solely steal for personal
gain.

What is the Tower of Lachery? It is a tower that
has been standing in the Disodart continent for a
long time. It is located to the west of the
capital city. It is said to have been built to
seal away ancient demons.

Regarding the  \c[2]races\c[0], in Disodart, there
are mainly the Human race, Doggy race, Elf race,
Lewd Demon race, Dark race, and Panda race. The
creatures with strong breeding activities are
referred to as Lustful Beasts.
